oai_dc:dc.dc:title: It may be YOUR practice, but it's OUR business!
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Gardiner, Mark
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: practice management
VCPR
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This presentation details the long-term, trusted relationship between a beef producer and the local veterinarian. The veterinarian is a source of new, innovative information to help keep the ranch successful and a model for modern ranching practices.
